content: Just secured some seed funding for the Xander startup. It's happening! Sarah's been my sounding board through all this. We're setting up a home office, making space for both our dreams to grow.

Xander's user base is growing, and so is our understanding of AI's role in finance. Sarah and I had a tech-free day, just to remind ourselves there's more to life than screens. The balance is what keeps us grounded and moving forward.
